  defaultYesLabel: Yes
  defaultNoLabel: No
  charsPerSecond: 40
  holdToFastTypeMultiplier: 5
  introText: 'i the back of the garden you spot a shiny object that catches your
    eyes '
  nodes:
  - question: You spot a well crafted axe in the far corner of the garden, it looks
      out of place.
    yesReply: 'Dhampir: The preist doesn''t look like the type to chop wood... '
    noReply: 'Dhampir: what is this doing here? '
    nextAfterYes: 1
    nextAfterNo: 2
    yesLabel: sus
    noLabel: question
    minutesOnEnter: 0
    minutesOnYes: 10
    minutesOnNo: 10
    mcOnYes: 0
    mcOnNo: 0
    enemyOnYes: 0
    enemyOnNo: 3
    affectsAlignment: 0
    humansOnYes: 0
    undeadOnYes: 0
    humansOnNo: 0
    undeadOnNo: 0
  - question: the further you look at it the more this axe reminds you of something
      you onc saw in your book, the craftmanship of it seems very reconizable...
    yesReply: ' '
    noReply: "\n "
    nextAfterYes: -1
    nextAfterNo: -1
    yesLabel: 
    noLabel: 
    minutesOnEnter: 0
    minutesOnYes: 0
    minutesOnNo: 0
    mcOnYes: 0
    mcOnNo: 0
    enemyOnYes: 0
    enemyOnNo: 0
    affectsAlignment: 0
    humansOnYes: 0
    undeadOnYes: 10
    humansOnNo: 10
    undeadOnNo: 0
  - question: The more you wonder abou this axe, the more dispair seeps into your
      soul... you could end it all right now. no more suffering, no more lies, no
      more pain... only peace...
    yesReply: "You pick the axe up a raises it above your head, you are think about
      your life and all the suffering you\xF8ve had to endure...\n\nDhampir: i cant
      go on lke this.\n\nYou start a count down\n1... you hesitate\n2... is this
      really ahppening\n3... You swing the axe a you h-\n\nRookie: .... What are
      you doing? that seems counter productive... idiot "
    noReply: 'No i shouldnt do it, i cant do it. my task on this earth is to help....
      no matter the cost. '
    nextAfterYes: 1
    nextAfterNo: 1
    yesLabel: Kill yourself
    noLabel: put the axe away
